Packages
com.abcodeworks.webshortcututil.read Provides classes for reading web shortcut files
com.abcodeworks.webshortcututil.write Provides classes for creating web shortcut files

 

A Java library for reading and writing web shortcut files.

This module is part of the WebShortcutUtil suite. For more details see the main website.

See the read and write packages for usage details.

A brief list of the supported shortcut types:

  • .desktop - Free Desktop shortcut (used by Linux)
  • .url - Used by Windows
  • .website - Used by Windows
  • .webloc - Used by Apple/Mac/OSX

Source Code https://github.com/abcodeworks/WebShortcutUtil-Java
